rows ---> outer loop
columns ---> inner loop


Print the pattern:
* * * * *
* * * * *
* * * * *
* * * * *


Main.java
~~~~~~~~~~~
import java.util.*;

public class Main{
    public static void main(String args[]) {
        int n = 4;
        int m = 5;

        // outer loop
        for(int i=1; i <= n; i++) {
            // inner loop
            for(int j = 1; j <= m; j++) {
                System.out.print("* ");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}

